items.title: El Monstro..
items.description:
Captain Creepy posted a photo:

Bought this sign as a warning to anyone coming up the stairs to our apartment...

"El Monstro" WILL bite and leave marks on you...

Do Not Enter Unprotected!!!... the items we recommend you bring with you but not limited to, are:

Holy Water,
a Crucifix,
a water pistol,
a .45 cal automatic with silver bullets,
melee weapons of any kind(they won't help you anyway,)...
some steak,(he seems to love red meat)

and a large squeak toy.

Good Luck!!
items.author: nobody@flickr.com ("Captain Creepy")
